description:
Who are the victims and villains? Amber Heard, Sam Asghari, and Jada Pinkett Smith… Yeah no, we DON’T know!


In todays episode we chat all things current in pop culture right now! Also find out what do Johnny Depp and Kristen Leanne have in common?

Are you team Jonny or team Amber?

The true question is…. will this be the day that Amber Heard almost caught Captain Jack Sparrow?!


Do all the things and share us with your friends.

Also if you share us on Instagram don’t forget to tag us do we can repost you! ❤️


We are also on Spotify, Apple Podcast and more! Search "Yeah No I Know".

* Everything we talk about on this podcast is our own individual opinions, not fact. Research everything for yourself and make the best decisions for you.
